
=====================================================================
 
TABLE DESCRIPTION  :  File Definition include for Patient * 
                      GST Financial Lumpsum Revenue breakdown 
                      (Accommodation records only)
  
TABLE NAME         :  patrfgaf
=====================================================================
DFINSYS     char        1     1   SYSTEM INDICATOR  
                                   1 = A + E  
                                   2 = Outpatient  
                                   3 = Inpatient  
                                   4 = Other Financial  
                                   5 = Day Centre  
FINSITE     char        6     2   OUTPATIENT SITE  
FINYEAR     char        4     8   FINANCIAL YEAR  
FINTYPE     char        1    12   FINANCIAL TYPE  
                                   A - FEES GENERATED  
                                   B - CASH RECEIVED  
                                   C - JOURNALS  
                                   D - MERCHANT CARDS - CLAIMED  
                                   E - MERCHANT CARDS - PAID  
                                   F - MERCHANT CARDS - COMMIS  
                                   G - MERCHANT CARDS - JOUR  
FINCODE     char       13    13   FINANCE CODE  
                                   AXXXYYYZZZTTT  
                                   NXXXYYYZZZTTT - Credit Note  
                                   A - A fixed char  
                                   N - A fixed char for Credit Note  
                                   XXX - Revenue breakdown code (category FI)  
                                   If category FI - TCINDC2=A  
                                   - Accommodation  
                                   (system parameter CACCFEE)  
                                   XXX - Breakdown Code for accommodation  
                                   YYYZZZTTT - ACCOMMODATION  
                                   YYY - ADMISS TYPE  
                                   OR WARD  
                                   ZZZ - BLANK OR  
                                   CLAIM TYPE  
                                   or  
                                   YYYZZZ - ACCOMODATION  
                                   YYY - WARD  
                                   ZZZ - CLAIM  
                                   TTT - ADMISSION TYPE  
                                   If TCINDC2<>A  
                                   - Miscellaneous item  
                                   TXXX  
                                   PXXX - Credit Note  
                                   T - A fixed char  
                                   P - A fixed char for Credit Note  
                         XXX - Breakdown code for Miscellaneous Category Code  
       If breakdown code does not exist, the fincode will be setup as follow:  
                                   XAAAAAAAAABBB  
                                   ZAAAAAAAAABBB - Credit Note  
                                   X - A fixed char  
                                   Z - A fixed char for Credit Note  
                                   AAAAAAAAA - Casemix code  
                                   BBB - First three char of Health fund  
                               Y <spaces> - only for "To Be Invoiced section"  
                         Y - A fixed char for Casemix payment accrual balance  
              - the difference between the actual total of lumpsum amount and  
                                   the total amount of revenues breakdown.  
FINPER      decimal   14,2   26   PERIOD AMOUNT  
FINMTH1     decimal   14,2   34   AMOUNT FOR MONTH 1  
