FINMTH12    decimal   14,2  122   AMOUNT FOR MONTH 12  
FINMTH13    decimal   14,2  130   AMOUNT FOR MONTH 13 (!)  
FLSTYR      decimal   14,2  138   LAST YEAR AMT SINCE LAST YEAR  
FINHOSP     char        3   146   Hospital ID (pathspaf)  
